column1: Rutger, Kane & the PSPCA Thank All the Lifters and Attendees of PowerPalooza 12 who donated money and much needed toys, food and snacks.

RPS rounded up the over $300 of cash donations to $500, and presented it to the PSPCA shelter in Hunting Park, Philadelpia in the name of the Lifters of PowerPalooza 12 on April 22. At that time there were still 19 dogs crated in the auxiliary barn, because areas of the shelter were not yet cleared for the viruses that have plagued the facility for more than 5 years.
